WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.847
Celebrating one thousand days without
Instagram!

00:03.147 --> 00:05.707
Citizens report unusual symptoms:

00:06.007 --> 00:07.444
actual conversations.

00:07.744 --> 00:09.886
I had to speak with my parents.

00:10.186 --> 00:11.414
The horror!

00:11.714 --> 00:14.274
Internet overuse is a real problem.

00:14.574 --> 00:17.134
Smoke signals offer a charming
alternative.

00:17.434 --> 00:20.360
Astonishing discoveries are being made
offline.

00:20.660 --> 00:23.820
Next, we learn to appreciate life
unplugged.

00:24.120 --> 00:27.229
Life offline offers unexpected rewards.

00:27.529 --> 00:30.977
Face-to-face interactions are surprisingly
fulfilling.

00:31.277 --> 00:34.046
The world is full of wonders beyond the
screen.

00:34.346 --> 00:37.272
Simple pleasures become profoundly
meaningful.

00:37.572 --> 00:40.759
I rediscovered the joy of reading physical
books.

00:41.059 --> 00:44.037
The quiet moments are surprisingly
enriching.

00:44.337 --> 00:46.505
I am more present in my life.

00:46.805 --> 00:48.999
I appreciate the small things.

00:49.299 --> 00:51.807
This experience has been transformative.

00:52.107 --> 00:54.536
My relationships have deepened
significantly.

